#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.57"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.57:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.57:0.2"
msgid "6. Dukkhavagga"
msgstr "6. Suffering"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.57:0.3"
msgid "57. Taruṇarukkhasutta"
msgstr "57. A Sapling"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.57:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn12.57:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Saṃyojaniyesu, bhikkhave, dhammesu assādānupassino viharato taṇhā "
"pavaḍḍhati."
msgstr ""
"“There are things that are prone to being fettered. When you concentrate on "
"the gratification provided by these things, your craving grows."

msgctxt "sn12.57:1.3"
msgid "Taṇhāpaccayā upādānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Craving is a condition for grasping. …"

msgctxt "sn12.57:1.4"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.57:2.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, taruṇo rukkho."
msgstr "Suppose there was a sapling."

#. VAR: palimajjeyya → palisattheyya (bj) | palisajjeyya (s1-3, km, pts1-2) | palipaṭṭheyya (mr) | palibandheyya (ṭīkānurūpaṃ)
msgctxt "sn12.57:2.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa puriso kālena kālaṃ mūlāni palimajjeyya kālena kālaṃ paṃsuṃ dadeyya, "
"kālena kālaṃ udakaṃ dadeyya."
msgstr ""
"And from time to time someone would clear around the roots, supply soil, and "
"water it."

msgctxt "sn12.57:2.3"
msgid ""
"Evañhi so, bhikkhave, taruṇo rukkho tadāhāro tadupādāno vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjeyya."
msgstr ""
"Fueled and sustained in this way the sapling would grow, increase, and "
"mature."

msgctxt "sn12.57:2.4"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, saṃyojaniyesu dhammesu assādānupassino viharato "
"taṇhā pavaḍḍhati."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, there are things that are prone to being fettered. When you "
"concentrate on the gratification provided by these things, your craving "
"grows."

msgctxt "sn12.57:2.5"
msgid "Taṇhāpaccayā upādānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Craving is a condition for grasping. …"

msgctxt "sn12.57:2.6"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.57:3.1"
msgid ""
"Saṃyojaniyesu, bhikkhave, dhammesu ādīnavānupassino viharato taṇhā "
"nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"There are things that are prone to being fettered. When you concentrate on "
"the drawbacks of these things, your craving ceases."

msgctxt "sn12.57:3.2"
msgid "Taṇhānirodhā upādānanirodho … pe …"
msgstr "When craving ceases, grasping ceases. …"

msgctxt "sn12.57:3.3"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.90"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.57:4.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, taruṇo rukkho."
msgstr "Suppose there was a sapling."

msgctxt "sn12.57:4.2"
msgid "Atha puriso āgaccheyya kuddālapiṭakaṃ ādāya … pe …"
msgstr "Then a person comes along with a spade and basket. …"

msgctxt "sn12.57:4.3"
msgid "nadiyā vā sīghasotāya pavāheyya."
msgstr ""
"They’d cut the sapling apart, cut up the parts, and chop it into little "
"bits. They’d dry the bits in the wind and sun, burn them with fire, and "
"reduce them to ashes. Then they’d winnow the ashes in a strong wind, or "
"float them away down a swift stream."

msgctxt "sn12.57:4.4"
msgid ""
"Evañhi so, bhikkhave, taruṇo rukkho ucchinnamūlo assa tālāvatthukato "
"anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo."
msgstr ""
"In this way the sapling is cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, "
"obliterated, and unable to arise in the future."

msgctxt "sn12.57:4.5"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, saṃyojaniyesu dhammesu ādīnavānupassino viharato "
"taṇhā nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, there are things that are prone to being fettered. When you "
"concentrate on the drawbacks of these things, your craving ceases."

msgctxt "sn12.57:4.6"
msgid "Taṇhānirodhā upādānanirodho … pe …"
msgstr "When craving ceases, grasping ceases. …"

msgctxt "sn12.57:4.7"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī”ti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.57:4.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
